category: Perl
requires: perl perl-File-BaseDir perl-File-DesktopEntry shared-mime-info
sdesc: "Perl module for determining mime types using shared-mime-info"
ldesc: "This module can be used to determine the mime type of a file;
it's a replacement for File-MMagic trying to implement the freedesktop
specification for using the shared mime-info database. The package comes
with a script called 'mimetype' that can be used as a file(1)
work-alike."
